{{wiktionary|capella}}
'''[[Capella]]''' is a bright star in the constellation of Auriga.
'''Capella''' may also refer to: {{TOC right}} ==Places== * [[Capella, Queensland]], a town in the Central Highlands Region, Australia * [[Capella, Aragon]], a municipality in Huesca, Spain * [[Capella Island]], a minor island of the U.S. Virgin Islands
==Other uses== * [[Capella (crater)]], an impact crater on the Moon * [[Capella (engineering)]], an open-source engineering solution * [[Chapel (music)|Capella (music)]], a musical ensemble * [[Capella (notation program)]], a program by capella Software AG * [[Mazda Capella]], a model of automobile * [[USS Capella|USS ''Capella'']], a cargo ship of the United States Navy * [[Capella (concrete ship)]], a concrete ship built in World War II. * [[Capella Aircraft]], an American aircraft manufacturer * [[Capella University]], an online academic institution based in Minneapolis, Minnesota * ''[[Gallinago]]'' or ''Capella'', a genus of snipes * [[Capella Resort, Singapore]], a hotel in Singapore
==People with the name== * [[Martianus Capella]], writer and astronomer of late antiquity * [[Tom Capella]], American politician
